    "attributes": {
        "action": "Issue different vehicle registration marks for BEVs (Electric Vehicles).",
        "additional_details": "It helps law enforcement if plates easily distinguished and memorable. This scheme doesn't jeopardise that as 2 and Z are similar, and 7 and V both have diagonal components",
        "background": "Awareness of the increasing number of BEVs on UK roads, may greatly help the Government's shift towards vehicles with no direct CO2 or other emissions. From March next year, new BEVs should be given the year designator Z0 instead of 20. Then in September V0 instead of 70. Special case for a decade",
